results.name: Continued fraction for sinh(gamma).
comment: Continued fraction of (exp(gamma)-exp(-gamma))/2 = sinh(gamma) (A147709), where gamma is the Euler-Mascheroni constant (A001620).
See A322602 for the continued fraction of cosh(gamma).
xref: Cf. A147709 (decimal expansion), A001620 (Euler-Mascheroni constant), A322602.
